summary:
I am passionate about my job. I strive to stay up to date with all new and upcoming innovations, especially the ones in my areas of focus.
I am an IT professional with several years of experience managing different technologies in a fast-paced environment. I have worked with UNIX/Linux as well as Windows Servers and administered hundreds of applications for Fortune 500 clients. 
I currently hold an ITIL certification and know my way around areas such as Incident, Problem, and Change management, and have a broad experience improving the success of my customers' business operation.
With my in-depth technical knowledge, I have the ability to diagnose and troubleshoot creative solutions to unique problems.
